Summary: Moving flickering lights just above treeline than just disappeared.
divs: sighting detailswhile watching tv,i saw strange looking lights in the sky,just above or at top of tree line.we live on a ridge(probably highest land in county)and have two eight foot sliding glass doors with trapazoid windows above.needless to say i have an awsome veiw out of the front of our home.we look out over swamp and the tahquamenon river basin,there are no homes or anything out there.what i saw were lights flickering and moving from sw to ne verry slowly,somthing just did not seem right about the lights and when i got up to get a better look they\it just disappeared.there where no clouds in the sky at this time,lots of stars,couse at first thats what i thought,it just went behind a cloud,but there wernt any.
